Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.11,0:22:14.48,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感情的代名词
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.93,0:22:18.49,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不胜枚举
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.71,0:22:22.10,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}若你的眼神在呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.30,0:22:26.16,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我便靠本能来判断
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.16,0:22:26.75,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Trust　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.75,0:22:28.01,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}纠葛难分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.01,0:22:28.66,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Trash　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.66,0:22:33.40,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}光明与黑暗 相随相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.40,0:22:37.34,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}仿若珍珠 连成一串
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.34,0:22:41.35,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自有缘由
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.08,0:22:45.80,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}偶然也好 自然也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.80,0:22:50.52,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}终将化作期待的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.57,0:22:54.24,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}心的温度
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.36,0:22:57.09,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}开始渐渐上升
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.22,0:23:01.10,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有伪装 亦无需试探
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.10,0:23:05.66,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}做最真的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.86,0:23:09.64,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}坚守信仰 不离不弃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.64,0:23:13.25,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好想告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.25,0:23:15.09,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Be my reason
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.09,0:23:17.09,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}陪在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.09,0:23:19.94,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Be my further future
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.13,0:21:56.94,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Be my reason
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.94,0:21:59.00,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}すべてが今
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.03,0:22:01.35,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Be my further future
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.35,0:22:02.79,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}動き出す
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.81,0:22:04.22,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Be my reason
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.65,0:22:06.38,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君のそばで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.60,0:22:08.96,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Be my further future
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.11,0:22:14.48,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感情の名前なんて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.93,0:22:18.49,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}言い出せばキリがないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.71,0:22:22.10,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君の目が叫ぶのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.30,0:22:26.16,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本能で聞き分ける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.16,0:22:26.75,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Trust
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.75,0:22:28.01,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}付き纏う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.01,0:22:28.66,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Trash
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.66,0:22:33.40,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そこにある 光も闇も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.40,0:22:37.34,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}つながりだす ビーズのように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.34,0:22:41.35,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}理由があるから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.08,0:22:45.80,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}偶然でも 成り行きでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.80,0:22:50.52,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}信じたい出会いに変わってく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.57,0:22:54.24,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}心の温度が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.36,0:22:57.09,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少しずつ上がるね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.22,0:23:01.10,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}見せかけじゃない 駆け引きもない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.10,0:23:05.66,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本当の自分のままで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.86,0:23:09.64,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}選んだ場所に立ってること
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.64,0:23:13.25,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君に伝えたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.25,0:23:15.09,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Be my reason
